         <tr>
          <td align="center" bgcolor="#bad598" style="padding:0;Margin:0;background-color:#bad598">
           <table class="es-content-body" cellspacing="0" cellpadding="0" bgcolor="#ffffff" align="center" role="none" style="mso-table-lspace:0pt;mso-table-rspace:0pt;border-collapse:collapse;border-spacing:0px;background-color:#FFFFFF;width:600px">
             <tr>
              <td align="left" style="padding:0;Margin:0;padding-top:20px;padding-left:20px;padding-right:20px">
               <table width="100%" cellspacing="0" cellpadding="0" role="none" style="mso-table-lspace:0pt;mso-table-rspace:0pt;border-collapse:collapse;border-spacing:0px">
                 <tr>
                  <td valign="top" align="center" style="padding:0;Margin:0;width:560px">
                   <table width="100%" cellspacing="0" cellpadding="0" role="presentation" style="mso-table-lspace:0pt;mso-table-rspace:0pt;border-collapse:collapse;border-spacing:0px">
                     <tr>
                      <td align="left" style="padding:0;Margin:0"><p style="Margin:0;-webkit-text-size-adjust:none;-ms-text-size-adjust:none;mso-line-height-rule:exactly;font-family:arial, 'helvetica neue', helvetica, sans-serif;line-height:21px;color:#333333;font-size:14px">Thank you for volunteering as a virtual host for Housing Hope benefitting The Mary Parrish Center.<br><br>This email contains all of the details you need to manage your public host page and see the progress of your personal campaign.<br><br>If you have problems at any time, you can email Brannan Atkinson at <a href="mailto:brannan@amyacommunications.com" style="-webkit-text-size-adjust:none;-ms-text-size-adjust:none;mso-line-height-rule:exactly;text-decoration:underline;color:#2CB543;font-size:14px">brannan@amyacommunications.com</a>. He will get back to you quickly.</p><p style="Margin:0;-webkit-text-size-adjust:none;-ms-text-size-adjust:none;mso-line-height-rule:exactly;font-family:arial, 'helvetica neue', helvetica, sans-serif;line-height:21px;color:#333333;font-size:14px"><br></p><h2 style="Margin:0;line-height:28.8px;mso-line-height-rule:exactly;font-family:'playfair display', georgia, 'times new roman', serif;font-size:24px;font-style:normal;font-weight:normal;color:#333333">Your Public Page</h2><p style="Margin:0;-webkit-text-size-adjust:none;-ms-text-size-adjust:none;mso-line-height-rule:exactly;font-family:arial, 'helvetica neue', helvetica, sans-serif;line-height:21px;color:#333333;font-size:14px"><br></p><p style="Margin:0;-webkit-text-size-adjust:none;-ms-text-size-adjust:none;mso-line-height-rule:exactly;font-family:arial, 'helvetica neue', helvetica, sans-serif;line-height:21px;color:#333333;font-size:14px">The address for your public page is <a href="https://www.housinghopenashville.org/hosts/{{ $user->host_url }}" style="-webkit-text-size-adjust:none;-ms-text-size-adjust:none;mso-line-height-rule:exactly;text-decoration:underline;color:#2CB543;font-size:14px">https://www.housinghopenashville.org/hosts/{{ $user->host_url }}</a>. This is the page you will share via email and on social media.<br><br>When people visit your personal page, the Housing Hope website will set a cookie that helps ensure you are credited as the host –&nbsp;which is exactly what we want.<br><br>Right now, the only information on your public page is your name and a link to the Giving Catalog (our ecommerce store).<br><br>You have the option of adding any of the following information:</p>
                       <ul>
                        <li style="-webkit-text-size-adjust:none;-ms-text-size-adjust:none;mso-line-height-rule:exactly;font-family:arial, 'helvetica neue', helvetica, sans-serif;line-height:21px;Margin-bottom:15px;margin-left:0;color:#333333;font-size:14px"><p style="Margin:0;-webkit-text-size-adjust:none;-ms-text-size-adjust:none;mso-line-height-rule:exactly;font-family:arial, 'helvetica neue', helvetica, sans-serif;line-height:21px;color:#333333;font-size:14px">A photo</p></li>
                        <li style="-webkit-text-size-adjust:none;-ms-text-size-adjust:none;mso-line-height-rule:exactly;font-family:arial, 'helvetica neue', helvetica, sans-serif;line-height:21px;Margin-bottom:15px;margin-left:0;color:#333333;font-size:14px"><p style="Margin:0;-webkit-text-size-adjust:none;-ms-text-size-adjust:none;mso-line-height-rule:exactly;font-family:arial, 'helvetica neue', helvetica, sans-serif;line-height:21px;color:#333333;font-size:14px">The total amount you have raised to date</p></li>
                        <li style="-webkit-text-size-adjust:none;-ms-text-size-adjust:none;mso-line-height-rule:exactly;font-family:arial, 'helvetica neue', helvetica, sans-serif;line-height:21px;Margin-bottom:15px;margin-left:0;color:#333333;font-size:14px"><p style="Margin:0;-webkit-text-size-adjust:none;-ms-text-size-adjust:none;mso-line-height-rule:exactly;font-family:arial, 'helvetica neue', helvetica, sans-serif;line-height:21px;color:#333333;font-size:14px">A goal that you set</p></li>
                        <li style="-webkit-text-size-adjust:none;-ms-text-size-adjust:none;mso-line-height-rule:exactly;font-family:arial, 'helvetica neue', helvetica, sans-serif;line-height:21px;Margin-bottom:15px;margin-left:0;color:#333333;font-size:14px"><p style="Margin:0;-webkit-text-size-adjust:none;-ms-text-size-adjust:none;mso-line-height-rule:exactly;font-family:arial, 'helvetica neue', helvetica, sans-serif;line-height:21px;color:#333333;font-size:14px">A list of the items that people have given when crediting you the host</p></li>
                        <li style="-webkit-text-size-adjust:none;-ms-text-size-adjust:none;mso-line-height-rule:exactly;font-family:arial, 'helvetica neue', helvetica, sans-serif;line-height:21px;Margin-bottom:15px;margin-left:0;color:#333333;font-size:14px"><p style="Margin:0;-webkit-text-size-adjust:none;-ms-text-size-adjust:none;mso-line-height-rule:exactly;font-family:arial, 'helvetica neue', helvetica, sans-serif;line-height:21px;color:#333333;font-size:14px">A message about why you are supporting Housing Hope</p></li>
                       </ul><p style="Margin:0;-webkit-text-size-adjust:none;-ms-text-size-adjust:none;mso-line-height-rule:exactly;font-family:arial, 'helvetica neue', helvetica, sans-serif;line-height:21px;color:#333333;font-size:14px">And, you can update these options at any time. For example, you may want to share your host total after donors start giving. You can turn that and other options on or off at any time.<br><br></p><h2 style="Margin:0;line-height:28.8px;mso-line-height-rule:exactly;font-family:'playfair display', georgia, 'times new roman', serif;font-size:24px;font-style:normal;font-weight:normal;color:#333333">Accessing Your Dashboard</h2><p style="Margin:0;-webkit-text-size-adjust:none;-ms-text-size-adjust:none;mso-line-height-rule:exactly;font-family:arial, 'helvetica neue', helvetica, sans-serif;line-height:21px;color:#333333;font-size:14px"><br></p><p style="Margin:0;-webkit-text-size-adjust:none;-ms-text-size-adjust:none;mso-line-height-rule:exactly;font-family:arial, 'helvetica neue', helvetica, sans-serif;line-height:21px;color:#333333;font-size:14px">Your dashboard is private and only for you. The dashboard is where you can customize your profile and see the progress of your personal campaign.</p><p style="Margin:0;-webkit-text-size-adjust:none;-ms-text-size-adjust:none;mso-line-height-rule:exactly;font-family:arial, 'helvetica neue', helvetica, sans-serif;line-height:21px;color:#333333;font-size:14px"><br></p><p style="Margin:0;-webkit-text-size-adjust:none;-ms-text-size-adjust:none;mso-line-height-rule:exactly;font-family:arial, 'helvetica neue', helvetica, sans-serif;line-height:21px;color:#333333;font-size:14px"><b>**IMPORTANT**</b> You can change your password after you log in the first time. Look for the password reset at the bottom of the Edit Profile page.</p></td>
                     </tr>
                   </table></td>
                 </tr>
               </table></td>
             </tr>
             <tr>
              <td align="left" style="padding:0;Margin:0;padding-top:20px;padding-left:20px;padding-right:20px">
               <table cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" width="100%" role="none" style="mso-table-lspace:0pt;mso-table-rspace:0pt;border-collapse:collapse;border-spacing:0px">
                 <tr>
                  <td align="center" valign="top" style="padding:0;Margin:0;width:560px">
                   <table cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" width="100%" role="presentation" style="mso-table-lspace:0pt;mso-table-rspace:0pt;border-collapse:collapse;border-spacing:0px">
                     <tr>
                      <td align="center" style="padding:0;Margin:0;padding-bottom:15px"><h2 style="Margin:0;line-height:24px;mso-line-height-rule:exactly;font-family:arial, 'helvetica neue', helvetica, sans-serif;font-size:24px;font-style:normal;font-weight:normal;color:#333333">Username: {{ $user->email }}</h2><h2 style="Margin:0;line-height:24px;mso-line-height-rule:exactly;font-family:arial, 'helvetica neue', helvetica, sans-serif;font-size:24px;font-style:normal;font-weight:normal;color:#333333">Password: WeLoveHousingHope</h2></td>
                     </tr>
                     <tr>
                      <td align="center" style="padding:0;Margin:0"><span class="es-button-border" style="border-style:solid;border-color:#2cb543;background:#539291;border-width:0px;display:inline-block;border-radius:30px;width:auto"><a href="https://housinghopenashville.org/dashboard" class="es-button" target="_blank" style="mso-style-priority:100 !important;text-decoration:none;-webkit-text-size-adjust:none;-ms-text-size-adjust:none;mso-line-height-rule:exactly;color:#FFFFFF;font-size:18px;padding:10px 20px 10px 20px;display:inline-block;background:#539291;border-radius:30px;font-family:arial, 'helvetica neue', helvetica, sans-serif;font-weight:normal;font-style:normal;line-height:21.6px;width:auto;text-align:center;mso-padding-alt:0;mso-border-alt:10px solid #539291">Login to Your Dashboard</a></span></td>
                     </tr>
                   </table></td>
                 </tr>
               </table></td>
             </tr>
             <tr>
              <td align="left" style="padding:0;Margin:0;padding-top:20px;padding-left:20px;padding-right:20px">
               <table cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" width="100%" role="none" style="mso-table-lspace:0pt;mso-table-rspace:0pt;border-collapse:collapse;border-spacing:0px">
                 <tr>
                  <td align="center" valign="top" style="padding:0;Margin:0;width:560px">
                   <table cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" width="100%" role="presentation" style="mso-table-lspace:0pt;mso-table-rspace:0pt;border-collapse:collapse;border-spacing:0px">
                     <tr>
                      <td align="left" style="padding:0;Margin:0"><p style="Margin:0;-webkit-text-size-adjust:none;-ms-text-size-adjust:none;mso-line-height-rule:exactly;font-family:arial, 'helvetica neue', helvetica, sans-serif;line-height:21px;color:#333333;font-size:14px">All the metrics on your dashboard will update in real-time as donor complete their donations. You are free to check your dashboard as often as you would like.<br><br>The list of every donor who credited you as the host will be listed on your dashboard.You will also receive an email each time a donor credits you as a host<br><br>You can change your password on the 'Edit Your Profile' page.</p><p style="Margin:0;-webkit-text-size-adjust:none;-ms-text-size-adjust:none;mso-line-height-rule:exactly;font-family:arial, 'helvetica neue', helvetica, sans-serif;line-height:21px;color:#333333;font-size:14px"><br></p><h2 style="Margin:0;line-height:28.8px;mso-line-height-rule:exactly;font-family:'playfair display', georgia, 'times new roman', serif;font-size:24px;font-style:normal;font-weight:normal;color:#333333">Editing Your Profile</h2><p style="Margin:0;-webkit-text-size-adjust:none;-ms-text-size-adjust:none;mso-line-height-rule:exactly;font-family:arial, 'helvetica neue', helvetica, sans-serif;line-height:21px;color:#333333;font-size:14px"><br></p><p style="Margin:0;-webkit-text-size-adjust:none;-ms-text-size-adjust:none;mso-line-height-rule:exactly;font-family:arial, 'helvetica neue', helvetica, sans-serif;line-height:21px;color:#333333;font-size:14px">As mentioned, you can edit almost everything on your public host page. To start, click the link "Edit your profile" toward the top of your dashboard.</p></td>
                     </tr>
                     <tr>
                      <td align="center" style="padding:0;Margin:0;padding-top:20px;padding-bottom:20px;font-size:0px"><img class="adapt-img" src="https://asset.cloudinary.com/brannanatkinson/7efa16e9a68fadcb608e75773adb2d75" alt style="display:block;border:0;outline:none;text-decoration:none;-ms-interpolation-mode:bicubic" width="560"></td>
                     </tr>
                     <tr>
                      <td align="left" style="padding:0;Margin:0;padding-bottom:20px"><p style="Margin:0;-webkit-text-size-adjust:none;-ms-text-size-adjust:none;mso-line-height-rule:exactly;font-family:arial, 'helvetica neue', helvetica, sans-serif;line-height:21px;color:#333333;font-size:14px">Options you can customize are as follows. Make sure to click the green buttons associated with several of the options, e.g. Save Photo.</p><p style="Margin:0;-webkit-text-size-adjust:none;-ms-text-size-adjust:none;mso-line-height-rule:exactly;font-family:arial, 'helvetica neue', helvetica, sans-serif;line-height:21px;color:#333333;font-size:14px"><br></p><h3 style="Margin:0;line-height:24px;mso-line-height-rule:exactly;font-family:arial, 'helvetica neue', helvetica, sans-serif;font-size:20px;font-style:normal;font-weight:normal;color:#333333">Photo</h3><p style="Margin:0;-webkit-text-size-adjust:none;-ms-text-size-adjust:none;mso-line-height-rule:exactly;font-family:arial, 'helvetica neue', helvetica, sans-serif;line-height:21px;color:#333333;font-size:14px">You can add or remove a photo from your profile.<br><br></p><h3 style="Margin:0;line-height:24px;mso-line-height-rule:exactly;font-family:arial, 'helvetica neue', helvetica, sans-serif;font-size:20px;font-style:normal;font-weight:normal;color:#333333">Host Total</h3><p style="Margin:0;-webkit-text-size-adjust:none;-ms-text-size-adjust:none;mso-line-height-rule:exactly;font-family:arial, 'helvetica neue', helvetica, sans-serif;line-height:21px;color:#333333;font-size:14px">This option shows the total donations raised when you are credited as the host.<br><br></p><h3 style="Margin:0;line-height:24px;mso-line-height-rule:exactly;font-family:arial, 'helvetica neue', helvetica, sans-serif;font-size:20px;font-style:normal;font-weight:normal;color:#333333">Goal</h3><p style="Margin:0;-webkit-text-size-adjust:none;-ms-text-size-adjust:none;mso-line-height-rule:exactly;font-family:arial, 'helvetica neue', helvetica, sans-serif;line-height:21px;color:#333333;font-size:14px">You can set a goal for yourself and then choose if you want to make that goal&nbsp;appear on your public profile. A private goal will only appear on your dashboard, not your public page. You do not have to set a goal if you do not want one.<br><br></p><h3 style="Margin:0;line-height:24px;mso-line-height-rule:exactly;font-family:arial, 'helvetica neue', helvetica, sans-serif;font-size:20px;font-style:normal;font-weight:normal;color:#333333">Show Donated Items</h3><p style="Margin:0;-webkit-text-size-adjust:none;-ms-text-size-adjust:none;mso-line-height-rule:exactly;font-family:arial, 'helvetica neue', helvetica, sans-serif;line-height:21px;color:#333333;font-size:14px">This option will show the specific Giving Catalog items donated when you are credited as the host. This option is useful if you want to encourage your audience to donate specific items and then track the progress of donations.<br><br></p><h3 style="Margin:0;line-height:24px;mso-line-height-rule:exactly;font-family:arial, 'helvetica neue', helvetica, sans-serif;font-size:20px;font-style:normal;font-weight:normal;color:#333333">Show Your Reason for Supporting Housing Hope</h3><p style="Margin:0;-webkit-text-size-adjust:none;-ms-text-size-adjust:none;mso-line-height-rule:exactly;font-family:arial, 'helvetica neue', helvetica, sans-serif;line-height:21px;color:#333333;font-size:14px">You can write any message you want to your audience. You can also update this message at any time during the Housing Hope campaign. Make sure to click the green "Save Message" button when you are ready to save your message.<br><br>You can change your password at the bottom of the page. Please note you will have to log in again after a password change.<br><br></p><h2 style="Margin:0;line-height:28.8px;mso-line-height-rule:exactly;font-family:'playfair display', georgia, 'times new roman', serif;font-size:24px;font-style:normal;font-weight:normal;color:#333333">Support</h2><h3 style="Margin:0;line-height:24px;mso-line-height-rule:exactly;font-family:arial, 'helvetica neue', helvetica, sans-serif;font-size:20px;font-style:normal;font-weight:normal;color:#333333"><br>For questions about your role as a host</h3><p style="Margin:0;-webkit-text-size-adjust:none;-ms-text-size-adjust:none;mso-line-height-rule:exactly;font-family:arial, 'helvetica neue', helvetica, sans-serif;line-height:21px;color:#333333;font-size:14px">Merrill Cope<br><a target="_blank" href="mailto:merrill@maryparrish.org" style="-webkit-text-size-adjust:none;-ms-text-size-adjust:none;mso-line-height-rule:exactly;text-decoration:underline;color:#2CB543;font-size:14px">merrill@maryparrish.org</a><br>(615) 438-1592<br><br></p><h3 style="Margin:0;line-height:24px;mso-line-height-rule:exactly;font-family:arial, 'helvetica neue', helvetica, sans-serif;font-size:20px;font-style:normal;font-weight:normal;color:#333333">For technical support with your dashboard or host profile</h3><p style="Margin:0;-webkit-text-size-adjust:none;-ms-text-size-adjust:none;mso-line-height-rule:exactly;font-family:arial, 'helvetica neue', helvetica, sans-serif;line-height:21px;color:#333333;font-size:14px">Brannan Atkinson<br><a href="mailto:brannan@amyacommunications.com" style="-webkit-text-size-adjust:none;-ms-text-size-adjust:none;mso-line-height-rule:exactly;text-decoration:underline;color:#2CB543;font-size:14px">brannan@amyacommunications.com</a><br>(615) 419.8483</p></td>
                     </tr>
